Pleased to meet with H.E. @antoniocostapm, Prime Minister of Portugal 🇵🇹.
 
We discussed 🇺🇳’s response to the war in Ukraine and on the impact of climate change on water management. 

Congratulated 🇵🇹 for the successful hosting of #OceansConference.
